        </item>
        <item>
            <title>小米 SU7 Ultra 量产版登场，1548 匹总输出被喻为地表最强四门量产车</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/01/xiaomi-su7-ultra-launch/life-tech/auto/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=xiaomi-su7-ultra-launch</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/01/xiaomi-su7-ultra-launch/life-tech/auto/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[duncan]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Sat, 01 Mar 2025 02:30:18 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[汽车科技]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SU7]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[SU7 Ultra]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[xiaomi]]>
            </category>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[小米]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294860</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>小米刚刚正式发表 SU7 Ultra 量产版，搭载超级三马达系统，总输出达 1,548 匹马力，零百加速仅需 1.98 秒，最高时速达 359.71 km/h。雷军形容其为「地表最强四门量产车」，目标直指 Tesla、Porsche 等豪华电动车品牌。新车售价为 52.99 万比早前预计降价近 30 万，小米创办人雷军解释希望可以重新定义新豪车，让喜欢的人买得起。</p><p><img fetchpriority="high" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294863" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8d1bb4a0f51b11efb7ff-694x466.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="466" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8d1bb4a0f51b11efb7ff-694x466.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/8d1bb4a0f51b11efb7ff.jpg 1182w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
小米 SU7 Ultra 原型车去年曾于德国纽伯林赛道，以 6 分 46.874 秒成绩打破四门车最快纪录，证明中国新能源车已能与全球顶级品牌竞争。雷军在「双 Ultra」发布会上表示，SU7 Ultra 是小米 15 年来最顶级的产品之一，并希望能在性能、科技、豪华体验上与 Porsche、Tesla、BBA（BMW、Benz、Audi）比肩。</p><p><img decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294862" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1cf0cd00f51b11efb7fa-694x414.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="414" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1cf0cd00f51b11efb7fa-694x414.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/1cf0cd00f51b11efb7fa.jpg 1280w" sizes="(max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SU7 Ultra 量产版提供「闪电黄、曜石黑、珍珠白、太空银、鹦鹉绿」五种车色，搭配银色拉花，并导入空气力学套件，包括大尺寸前铲、锻造轮毂（选配）、碳纤维固定式尾翼等。内装配备全新运动座椅、碳纤维方向盘，并大量使用 Alcantara 超细纤维布料，中控萤幕搭载专属 UI，提升驾驶体验。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294865" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/41972000f51b11efa95e-694x364.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="364" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/41972000f51b11efa95e-694x364.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/41972000f51b11efa95e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294864" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/30e6aa00f51b11ef9d7b-694x358.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="358" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/30e6aa00f51b11ef9d7b-694x358.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/30e6aa00f51b11ef9d7b.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>SU7 Ultra 采用三马达四驱系统，搭载两台小米超级马达 V8s 及一台小米超级马达 V6s，搭配，麒麟 2 代高效率电池，确保长时间高功率输出。其 0-100 km/h 加速仅需 1.98 秒，0-200 km/h 需时 5.86 秒，0-400 km/h 仅需 9.23 秒，性能已超越 Porsche Taycan Turbo。此外，小米创办人雷军戣调 SU7 Ultra 配备赛道级散热与陶瓷煞车系统，并搭载纽北调校底盘，即便标准版也能轻松应对赛道驾驶。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294866" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b59ef3b0f51b11efbf5e-694x335.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="335" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b59ef3b0f51b11efbf5e-694x335.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/b59ef3b0f51b11efbf5e.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><br />
雷军透露，小米汽车 2024 年交付目标为 30 万辆，而 SU7 Ultra 自去年底开放预订后，10 分钟内即收到 3,600 张订单，预计今年销量可达 1 万辆。SU7 Ultra 的推出，无疑加剧全球高性能电动车品牌的价格战。</p><p>来源: <a href="https://autos.yahoo.com.tw/news/%E5%9C%B0%E8%A1%A8%E6%9C%80%E9%80%9F%E3%80%81%E5%B0%8F%E7%B1%B3su7-ultra%E5%9B%9B%E9%96%80%E9%9B%BB%E5%8B%95%E8%B6%85%E8%B7%91%E7%8F%BE%E8%BA%AB%EF%BC%811548%E5%8C%B9%E9%A6%AC%E5%8A%9B%E3%80%81%E9%9B%B6%E7%99%BE%E5%8A%A0%E9%80%9F%E5%83%85%E9%9C%80198%E7%A7%92%EF%BC%8C%E5%94%AE%E5%83%B9%E4%B8%8D%E5%88%B0240%E8%90%AC%E5%85%83%EF%BC%81-012850706.html">yahoo</a></p><br /><b>
]]>
            </description>
            <wfw:commentRss>https://unwire.hk/2025/03/01/xiaomi-su7-ultra-launch/life-tech/auto/feed/</wfw:commentRss>
