        </item>
        <item>
            <title>《MHW》PS5 Pro vs PS5 大比拚，值得为芒亨升级 PS5 Pro？</title>
            <link>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/?utm_source=rss&#038;utm_medium=rss&#038;utm_campaign=ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw</link>
            <comments>https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/#respond</comments>
            <dc:creator>
                <![CDATA[Lawton]]>
            </dc:creator>
            <pubDate>Fri, 28 Feb 2025 15:36:33 +0000</pubDate>
            <category>
                <![CDATA[游戏情报]]>
            </category>
            <guid isPermaLink="false">https://unwire.hk/?p=1294804</guid>
            <description>
                <![CDATA[<p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》正式推出，相信好多朋友都准备为此大作做好准备，包括是否适合在这个时候升级 PS5 Pro。在正式版本中，PS5 Pro 专用的画质提升功能正式引入，在早前测试版我们还未能作出结论，但今次正式版我们终可正式来比较一下。总括来说，PS5 与 PS5 Pro 在画质、光影效果及整体流畅度方面均存在明显差距，如果用家希望在 PlayStation 平台享受本作，不打算 DIY 砌机电脑的话，就可留意以下介绍，考虑 PS5 Pro 购入的可能性。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294872" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05186.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><h2>测试影片：</h2><p><iframe loading="lazy" style="border: none; overflow: hidden;" src="https://www.facebook.com/plugins/video.php?height=476&amp;href=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2Funwirehk%2Fvideos%2F3969945699943116%2F&amp;show_text=false&amp;width=267&amp;t=0" width="500" height="776" frameborder="0" scrolling="no" allowfullscreen="allowfullscreen"></iframe><br />
&nbsp;</p><h2>三种模式该如何选择？</h2><p>《Monster Hunter Wilds》的 PlayStation 5 版本共提供三种模式，分别为：</p><ul><li>「帧率优先」模式：以稳定帧率为主要目标</li><li>「解析度优先」模式：全力提升画面解析度</li><li>「重视平衡」模式：在画面与帧率之间取得折衷</li></ul><p>虽然三个模式在 PS5 及 PS5 Pro 上的名称与功能一致，但实际体验却存在极大差异。尤其当画面细节、光影效果及帧率稳定性一并比较时，PS5 Pro 的优势更为显著。以下将会慢慢讲解。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294875" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05194.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲Monster Hunter Wild 显示设定</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294877" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲内有 3 个模式：解析度优先、重视平衡、帧率优先</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294878" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05195.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲另外亦有 120Hz 更新率输出支援（留意并不是指 120fps 进行游戏），在 PS5 Pro 上可获得更为流畅的画面</p><h2>「帧率优先」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>兼顾画质与流畅，<b>PS5 </b>仅能求稳</h2><p>顾名思义，「帧率优先」以优先确保稳定帧率为核心目标，两部主机均以 60fps 为目标。然而 PS5 Pro 与 PS5 之间的画面表现差距，在此模式已经非常明显。PS5 Pro 在该模式下几乎可全程维持 60fps，即使场景复杂，窒画面（突然大幅明显帧数下降）情况亦极少发生。这方面玩家可以放心进行游戏。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294879" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05191.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>例子 1：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294811" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895323-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲测试场景（图为 PS5 Pro 帧率优先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294809" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_-657x580.jpg" alt="" width="657" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_-657x580.jpg 657w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_pro_.jpg 922w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 657px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294810" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2-614x580.jpg" alt="" width="614" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2-614x580.jpg 614w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/ps5_2.jpg 792w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 614px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲对比之下，树木的沟造以及角色背后的纹理，都是 PS5 Pro 清楚得多</p><p>画质方面，PS5 采用动态解析度（Dynamic Resolution Scaling, DRS）技术，内部渲染范围约在 720p 至 1080p，通过空间升频和后期锐化处理输出到 4K 显示器。而 PS5 Pro 最大优势在于其具备 PSSR（PlayStation Spectral Super Resolution）技术辅助，透过 AI 升频技术有效提升画面清晰度，即使渲染解像度仅为 1080p，经 PSSR 处理后整体画面依然清晰干净。无论是树叶边缘、角色细节，还是远方地形纹理，均比 PS5 清楚许多，且树叶闪烁与锯齿问题大幅减少。</p><p>相较之下，PS5 虽然同样以 60fps 为目标，但面对较为复杂场景，例如大量魔物同时出现，或大面积水面反射时，帧率偶尔会下降至 50 几 fps。</p><p>例子 2：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294812" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/2025022895945-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲测试场景（图为 PS5 Pro 帧率优先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294813" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452-608x580.jpg" alt="" width="608" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452-608x580.jpg 608w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_9_59_452.jpg 904w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 608px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294815" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1-540x580.jpg" alt="" width="540" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1-540x580.jpg 540w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_00_102-1.jpg 814w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 540px" /></p><h2>游玩体验比较</h2><p>PS5 整体画面较为粗糙，远景物件轮廓模糊，尤其是沙漠场景中，沙地与岩石颜色相近，画面锐利度不足，导致玩家需要额外花时间辨认场景中的关键物件，对战斗专注度造成一定影响。</p><h2>「解析度优先」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>画质细致突出，<b>PS5 </b>画面模糊难辨</h2><p>这个模式是以展现游戏最高画质为目标。所以不论是 PS5 Pro 或者 PS5，都未能达到有 60fps 或以上的水平。对偏爱华丽画面的玩家来说，「解析度优先」模式无疑是画质爱好者的首选。在此模式下 PS5 Pro 与 PS5 之间的画质差距更为显著。PS5 Pro 的解析度最高可达 1944p，并同样透过 PSSR 提升画面整体细节表现，无论近景或远景均能保持极高画质。岩石表面纹理、铠甲反光质感、以及树叶层次感，均明显优于 PS5。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294880" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05193-1.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p>例子 1：</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294816" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228100553-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲测试场景（图为 PS5 Pro 解析度优先模式）</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294833" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2-613x580.jpg" alt="" width="613" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2-613x580.jpg 613w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_05_532-2.jpg 940w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 613px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294835" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1-567x580.jpg" alt="" width="567" height="580" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1-567x580.jpg 567w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-1.jpg 880w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 567px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲比对主角背后，PS5 Pro 解析度优先模式的画面清晰得多</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294837" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532-694x435.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="435" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532-694x435.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502283_10_05_532.jpg 1018w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294838" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2-694x397.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2-694x397.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_06_18-2.jpg 1086w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲远景景物也看到，PS5 Pro 悬崖边的纹理详细得多</p><p>相反 PS5 版本的动态解像度仅有 1080p 至 1440p 之间，加上缺少 PSSR，只能依赖传统空间升频（Spatial Upscaling）及后期锐化处理。整体画面较为柔和，甚至带有明显有一层「油膜」的感觉，树叶与场景物件边缘闪烁与锯齿问题在复杂场景中特别严重。</p><p>光影效果方面，PS5 Pro 在此模式下具备光线追踪（Ray Tracing）反射技术，水面光影反射效果更具层次感，水面看上去更加通透。特别是敌人经过水面时，会有明显很清晰的反射效果。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294840" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_33_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 解析度优先模式，看到的水面波纹涟漪都会较丰富，最大分别是敌人走过水面会产生倒影</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294839" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/202502228_10_37_13-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 解析度优先模式中，敌人走过倒影会十分浅，很难察觉（只有影子是一样的）看到的水面波纹涟漪都会较少，清澈度较低</p><p>反观 PS5，只能使用萤幕空间反射（SSR），不仅反射内容不完整，且画面细节模糊，感觉上水面会较为「污浊」。当部分反射面被遮挡时，倒影直接消失，敌人经过水面时反射效果也不特别明显，整体画面效果略显粗糙。</p><h2>游玩体验比较</h2><p>画质提升的代价便是流畅度明显下降。「解析度优先」模式之下，PS5 Pro 的体感帧率约为 30fps，即使 PS5 Pro 亦无法避免。角色移动、翻滚、攻击等操作皆明显失去流畅感，尤其面对高机动性魔物时，操作迟滞感格外明显。相信很多玩家都未必愿意在这样的流畅度下长期游玩。</p><h2>「重视平衡」模式：<b>PS5 Pro </b>表现均衡，<b>PS5 </b>勉强堪用</h2><p>「重视平衡」模式，为希望在画质与效能之间取得平衡的玩家而设，PS5 Pro 在此模式下的整体表现令人惊喜。PS5 Pro 该模式的解析度约为 1440p，经 PSSR 升频后，画面质感接近 「解析度优先」模式，约七成的水平。同时亦保留部分光线追踪反射效果。帧率目标为 40fps。至于 PS5，「重视平衡」模式的整体表现则略显尴尬。画质仅相当于 「解析度优先」模式，约五成水准，光线追踪反射功能完全取消，画面整体质感仅稍优于「帧率优先」模式。然而由于缺少 PSSR，画面仍偏柔和，细节表现一般。帧率目标为 40fps，但复杂场景时会降至 30fps 以下。</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294881" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05192.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294857" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_08_532-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294858" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_09_182-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 Pro 平衡模式较为精细</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294847" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_10_56_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294854" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-694x388.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="388" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-694x388.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_02_192-scaled.jpg 1280w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲PS5 平衡模式画面会较为柔和，而且流畅度会略逊于 PS5 Pro</p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294855" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082-685x580.jpg" alt="" width="469" height="397" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082-685x580.jpg 685w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_11_04_082.jpg 1063w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 469px" /></p><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter wp-image-1294856" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31-691x580.jpg" alt="" width="449" height="377" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31-691x580.jpg 691w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/20250228_211_05_31.jpg 924w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 449px" /></p><h2>游玩体验比较</h2><p>PS5 Pro 的平衡模式十分可取，整体流畅度明显优于 「解析度优先」模式。虽然不及「帧率优先」模式顺畅，但整体战斗体验依然属于可接受范围。偶尔出现掉帧，但对节奏影响不大。PS5 方面角色操作流畅度亦明显不如 「帧率优先」模式，整体战斗体验仅属堪用等级。</p><h2>总结：<b>PS5 Pro </b>全方位压倒<b> PS5</b></h2><p>综合三个模式比较，PS5 Pro 在《Monster Hunter Wilds》中的表现，无论画质、光影效果、还是帧率稳定性，皆明显优于 PS5。尤其光线追踪反射的加入，让场景真实感与沉浸感大幅提升，整体游玩体验更趋近于进入《Monster Hunter》世界的冒险旅程。</p><p>相对而言，PS5 玩家则需调整预期，若选择 「帧率优先」模式，尚可保有流畅战斗体验，但若贪图画质选择其他模式，画面模糊、细节缺失、反射效果不佳等问题，将直接影响整体狩猎体验。当场景内魔物数量增多或特效集中时，画面混乱且难以辨识敌我，整体操作手感亦明显不如 Pro 版。</p><table style="width: 100%;" cellspacing="0" cellpadding="0"><tbody><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top"><strong>模式</strong></td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top"><strong>解像度（动态）</strong></td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top"><strong>画质</strong></td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top"><strong>反射效果</strong></td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top"><strong>目标帧率</strong></td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top"><strong>真实体感</strong></td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top"><strong>游玩体验评语</strong></td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「帧率优先」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">约 1080p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">清晰，边缘平滑，少闪烁</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">60fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">55-60fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">画面干净又顺畅，最佳选择之一</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「帧率优先」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">约 720-1080p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">偏柔，锯齿明显，远景模糊</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">60fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">50-60fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">画质普通，但操作感顺畅，PS5 唯一推介</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「重视平衡」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">约 1440p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">近似 7 成 Resolution Mode 质感</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">光线追踪反射</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">40fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">35-40fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">兼顾画质与流畅，适合钟意靓画面又怕太 LAG 玩家</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「重视平衡」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">约 1080p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">解析度比 Frame Rate 高少少，但偏朦</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">40fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">30-40fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">画质普通，流畅度麻麻，冇乜优势</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「解析度优先」模式, PS5 Pro</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">1728p-1944p + PSSR</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">最高清细致</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">光线追踪反射</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">30fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">28-30fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">画面超靓，但操作感变重，适合影相党</td></tr><tr><td style="border-color: #d2d2fc; background-color: #d7fcf7; width: 17.317487%;" valign="top">「解析度优先」模式, PS5</td><td style="background-color: #ffe3e3; width: 12.393888%;" valign="top">1080p-1440p</td><td style="background-color: #e8ffe9; width: 22.071307%;" valign="top">偏柔偏朦，细节不清</td><td style="background-color: #fffedb; width: 8.064516%;" valign="top">SSR</td><td style="width: 5.432937%; background-color: #ebf7f7;" valign="top">30fps</td><td style="width: 5.517827%; background-color: #f0dae2;" valign="top">25-30fps</td><td style="width: 29.117148%;" valign="top">影相都嫌唔够靓，操作仲唔顺，唔推</td></tr></tbody></table><p><img loading="lazy" decoding="async" class="aligncenter size-medium wp-image-1294882" src="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190-694x463.jpg" alt="" width="694" height="463" srcset="https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190-694x463.jpg 694w, https://cdn.unwire.hk/wp-content/uploads/2025/02/dsc05190.jpg 1024w" sizes="auto, (max-width: 639px) 98vw, (max-width: 1199px) 64vw, 694px" /></p><p style="text-align: center;">▲今次由 ROG 借出电竞荧幕 ROG Swift OLED PG32UCDM 试玩 MHW。这个荧幕具有 4K 解像度的 32 吋超大画面，用上 OLED 技术画面对比度真的无得弹，0.03ms(GTG)、240Hz 更新率驳高阶电脑打机更爽快，当然无论驳 PS5 或者电脑都同样合适。官方建议零售价：HK$12,499</p><p>The post <a href="https://unwire.hk/2025/02/28/ps5-pro-vs-ps5-mhw/game-channel/">《MHW》PS5 Pro vs PS5 大比拚，值得为芒亨升级 PS5 Pro？</a> appeared first on <a href="https://unwire.hk">UNWIRE.HK</a>.</p>
